  "question": "How does the QR onboarding flow work?",
  "answer": "Open Smart Life, add a device from Camera&Lock, choose the observed Wi-Fi video lock family, select the network, place the lock in pairing mode, then present the QR from the phone to the lock camera and wait for confirmation."
